@Jim

I'm with you.  "The editors don't care about accuracy" is insulting not only to the editors, but to everyone who enjoys the word play that invariably comes with a little lose of "accuracy".

I don't want to do a puzzle in which every single clue and every single entry is pedantically pure.  I'm not even sure that's possible.   But if it were, it would be boring.

@Joe Horton
@Peter

