@Francis. These kind of themers are not worth my time, I have a full and busy life.   If you have time for them, terrific... more power to you.

I spend time on a crossword for the same reason everyone else does, they are fun and challenging.  Once the squares are all filled in though, I could care less about the themes.

Thanks for asking, I hope this is helpful to you.

